race.description: Midnite A Next Generation Betting App Handicap
race.comment: The Anthony Brittain yard appear to have turned a corner in recent months and BELLAGIO MAN (1) can continue wearing blinkers while completing a hat-trick following two nice wins over 1200m at Newcastle.  Going well and warrants plenty of thought. ANDALPROFIT (8) might prove the main danger on the back of a smooth Redcar (1200m) success earlier in the month. WICHAHPI (5) went well finishing runner-up tackling heavy ground at Nottingham last month. Cannot be ignored revisiting AW. ORBITAL CHIME (2) was denied a head attempting 1000m at Newcastle and could remain firmly involved back up in distance.
